t;&quot;&gt;M&amp;atilde; s&#7889; thu&#7871;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n            &lt;/td&gt;\r\n            &lt;td width=&quot;397&quot; style=&quot;width:297.55pt;border:solid #EEECE1 1.0pt;padding:3.75pt 3.75pt 3.75pt 3.75pt;\r\n            height:1.0pt&quot;&gt;\r\n            &lt;p style=&quot;mso-line-height-alt:1.0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:\r\n            9.0pt;font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;2300184009&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n            &lt;/td&gt;\r\n        &lt;/tr&gt;\r\n    &lt;/tbody&gt;\r\n&lt;/table&gt;\r\n&lt;/p&gt;','22/10/2011','25/06/2013','',24,7,3016,'huyennt',1,'ho-kinh-doanh-ngo-quoc-vung-bac-ninh-','&#273;&#7841;i l&yacute;, mikado ceramic, ph&acirc;n ph&#7889;i',NULL,NULL,NULL,'&#273;&#7841;i l&yacute;, mikado ceramic, ph&acirc;n ph&#7889;i',0,0,0,'','','admin',3,'Mikado',1,0,0,0),(27,'Ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung','Ph&oacute; Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ho&agrave;ng Trung H&#7843;i y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u trong qu&aacute; tr&igrave;nh tri&#7875;n khai th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&igrave;nh ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&ocirc;ng nung theo Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911;, B&#7897; X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng c&#7847;n nghi&ecirc;n c&#7913;u, ti&#7871;p thu nh&#7919;ng ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; c&#7911;a H&#7897;i V&#7853;t li&#7879;u X&acirc;y d&#7921;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam v&agrave; &#273;&#7873; xu&#7845;t, b&aacute;o c&aacute;o Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911; nh&#7919;ng v&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; v&#432;&#7907;t th&#7849;m quy&#7873;n','&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#432;&#7907;c bi&#7871;t, ng&amp;agrave;y 28/4/2010, Th&#7911; t&#432;&#7899;ng Ch&amp;iacute;nh ph&#7911; &#273;&amp;atilde; ph&amp;ecirc; duy&#7879;t ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#7871;n n&#259;m 2020.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;400&quot; height=&quot;261&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/gach-ngoi.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Theo Ch&#432;&#417;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh, s&#7869; c&amp;oacute; 3 ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;aacute;t tri&#7875;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng. &#272;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch xi m&#259;ng-c&#7889;t li&#7879;u, g&#7841;ch nh&#7865; v&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch kh&amp;aacute;c. Trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, t&#7927; l&#7879; g&#7841;ch xi m&#259;ng-c&#7889;t li&#7879;u tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng s&#7889; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung kho&#7843;ng 74% v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2015 v&amp;agrave; 70% v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2020.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch nh&#7865; (c&amp;oacute; 2 lo&#7841;i l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch t&#7915; b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng kh&amp;iacute; ch&#432;ng &amp;aacute;p v&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch t&#7915; b&amp;ecirc; t&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7885;t) chi&#7871;m t&#7927; l&#7879; v&amp;agrave;o kho&#7843;ng 21% v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2015 v&amp;agrave; 25% v&amp;agrave;o n&#259;m 2020 tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng s&#7889; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch kh&amp;aacute;c (&#273;&amp;aacute; ch&#7867;, g&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;aacute; ong, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung t&#7915; &#273;&#7845;t &#273;&#7891;i v&amp;agrave; ph&#7871; th&#7843;i x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng, g&#7841;ch silic&amp;aacute;t...) &#273;&#7841;t t&#7927; l&#7879; kho&#7843;ng 5% t&#7915; n&#259;m 2015 tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#7893;ng s&#7889; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7915; n&#259;m 2011, c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;igrave;nh nh&amp;agrave; cao t&#7847;ng (t&#7915; 9 t&#7847;ng tr&#7903; l&amp;ecirc;n) s&#7917; d&#7909;ng t&#7889;i thi&#7875;u 30% v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng nung lo&#7841;i nh&#7865; (kh&#7889;i l&#432;&#7907;ng th&#7875; t&amp;iacute;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng l&#7899;n h&#417;n 1000 kg/m3) trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/gach-ngoi.jpg',22,2,2078,'admin',1,'phat-trien-vat-lieu-xay-dung-khong-nung','v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&ocirc;ng nung, mikado, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'v&#7853;t li&#7879;u kh&ocirc;ng nung, mikado, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Theo website ch&iacute;nh ph&#7911;',1,1,0,1),(28,'10 c&aacute;ch ph&#7889;i m&agrave;u &#7889;p l&aacute;t g&#7841;ch men cho nh&agrave; t&#7855;m &#273;&#7865;p','&#272;&#7863;c &#273;i&#7875;m ri&ecirc;ng c&#7911;a nh&agrave; t&#7855;m l&agrave; &#7889;p g&#7841;ch men to&agrave;n b&#7897; &#273;&#7875; ch&#7889;ng &#7849;m m&#7889;c v&agrave; tr&#417;n tr&#432;&#7907;t. L&agrave;m th&#7871; n&agrave;o &#273;&#7875; ph&#7889;i m&agrave;u v&agrave; ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a g&#7841;ch men sao cho &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7845;t?','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-style-span&quot; style=&quot;font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; font-size: medium; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding-top: 5px; padding-right: 5px; padding-bottom: 5px; padding-left: 5px; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; &quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tham kh&#7843;o 10 c&amp;aacute;ch sau &#273;&amp;acirc;y:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1) B&#7843;ng m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&amp;aacute;y n&#432;&#7899;c&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7921;a nh&#432; &#273;&amp;aacute;y n&#432;&#7899;c s&amp;acirc;u m&#7897;t ng&amp;agrave;y n&#7855;ng, c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m 3,3&amp;times;3,6m n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7889;p b&#7857;ng nh&#7919;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch th&#7867; d&amp;agrave;i v&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; v&#7899;i s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u chuy&#7875;n bi&#7871;n &#7843;o di&#7879;u t&#7915; tr&#7855;ng xanh nh&#7841;t &#273;&#7871;n xanh th&#7851;m &#7903; ch&amp;acirc;n t&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2) H&amp;ograve;a tr&#7897;n nh&#7883;p nh&amp;agrave;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles01.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Xen k&#7869; nh&#7919;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch g&#7889;m m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7891;ng v&amp;agrave; n&amp;acirc;u s&#7851;m t&#7841;o ra m&#7897;t m&#7843;ng t&#432;&#7901;ng sang tr&#7885;ng ph&amp;iacute;a tr&amp;ecirc;n b&#7891;n r&#7917;a.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3) T&amp;ocirc;ng m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img width=&quot;450&quot; height=&quot;500&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles03.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;aacute;c s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a c&amp;acirc;y v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t trong m&#7897;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian bao g&#7891;m nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#273;a d&#7841;ng, t&#7915; g&#7841;ch mosaic th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng nh&#7887; d&#7865;t &#273;&#7871;n &#273;&amp;aacute; phi&#7871;n vu&amp;ocirc;ng v&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch men kh&amp;ocirc; c&#7905; to. Tuy v&#7853;y, ch&amp;uacute;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng b&#7883; r&#7889;i m&#7855;t hay ph&amp;ocirc; tr&#432;&#417;ng m&amp;agrave; v&#7851;n h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a v&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng: x&amp;aacute;m, xanh c&#7887; &amp;uacute;a, xanh d&#432;&#417;ng m&#7901;&amp;hellip; &#273;&#7873;u g&#7907;i nh&#7899; thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4) Nh&#7919;ng m&#7843;ng m&amp;agrave;u n&#7893;i b&#7853;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles04.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;ch ho&amp;agrave;n h&#7843;o &#273;&#7875; th&amp;ecirc;m m&#7897;t m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;agrave;o &#273;&amp;oacute; v&amp;agrave;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian t&#7855;m. G&#7841;ch men m&amp;agrave;u n&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t m&#7843;ng sang tr&amp;ecirc;n t&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;acirc;u, g&#7907;i nh&#7899; l&#7841;i khung tr&#7901;i c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng b&#7901; bi&#7875;n nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7899;i&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5) C&amp;acirc;u chuy&#7879;n c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch men&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles09.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Nh&#7919;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch g&#7889;m c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; l&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u cho m&#7897;t b&#7843;n t&amp;igrave;nh ca trong nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m. B&#7913;c ho&#7841; v&amp;ugrave;ng qu&amp;ecirc; Tuscan n&amp;agrave;y, &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7863;t trong m&#7897;t b&#7889;i c&#7843;nh r&#7921;c r&#7905; th&#7901;i Ph&#7909;c H&#432;ng, l&amp;agrave; t&amp;acirc;m &#273;i&#7875;m l&amp;agrave;m n&amp;ecirc;n n&amp;eacute;t sang tr&#7885;ng c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n c&#7911;a ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7855;m n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6) Nh&amp;agrave; ga metro&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles08.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Th&#7921;c s&#7921; l&amp;agrave; g&#7841;ch &#7889;p cho c&amp;aacute;c nh&amp;agrave; ga xe &#273;i&#7879;n ng&#7847;m hay h&#7847;m &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng b&#7897; r&#7845;t stylish. &#7902; &#273;&amp;acirc;y, c&amp;ugrave;ng v&#7899;i v&#7919;a mi&#7875;t m&#7841;ch m&amp;agrave;u x&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;, ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7855;m mang m&#7897;t v&#7867; l&#7841; l&#7851;m, v&#7915;a c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n v&#7915;a hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i, l&#7841;i r&#7845;t th&#7901;i trang.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7) Nh&#7919;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n cu&#7897;i b&amp;ecirc;n b&#7901; s&amp;ocirc;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles07.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&#272;&#7875; &amp;ldquo;nh&#7845;n m&#7841;nh t&#7847;m quan tr&#7885;ng&amp;rdquo; c&#7911;a s&amp;agrave;n cabin t&#7855;m &#273;&#7913;ng, tr&amp;ecirc;n s&amp;agrave;n n&#7873;n xi m&#259;ng , ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;atilde; cho l&amp;aacute;t nh&#7919;ng m&#7843;nh g&#7841;ch l&#7891;i gi&#7843; &#273;&amp;aacute; s&amp;ocirc;ng, r&#7845;t &#7845;n t&#432;&#7907;ng v&amp;agrave; ho&amp;agrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#432;&#7901;ng &#7889;p g&#7841;ch xanh &#273;&amp;aacute; nh&#7841;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8) &#272;&#432;&#7901;ng vi&#7873;n duy&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;aacute;ng&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles11.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Khi s&amp;agrave;n nh&amp;agrave; tr&#7889;ng qu&amp;aacute; r&#7897;ng, &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;aacute; v&#7905; s&#7921; bu&#7891;n t&#7867;, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; dung g&#7841;ch vi&#7873;n k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t &#7889;p th&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t &amp;ldquo;khung&amp;ldquo; hay m&#7897;t d&#7843;i g&#7847;n v&#7883; tr&amp;iacute; ch&amp;acirc;n t&#432;&#7901;ng bao ngo&amp;agrave;i. &#272;&#7863;c bi&#7879;t s&#7869; r&#7845;t sang tr&#7885;ng n&#7871;u &#273;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch th&#7911; c&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9) S&amp;aacute;ng t&#7841;o kh&amp;ocirc;ng bi&amp;ecirc;n gi&#7899;i&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles05.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ph&amp;aacute; v&#7905; b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng m&amp;agrave;u be, c&amp;aacute;c t&amp;ocirc;n m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a &#273;&#7845;t th&amp;ocirc;ng qua c&amp;aacute;c vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch kh&amp;aacute;c nhau &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng klinh ho&#7841;t. Thay v&amp;igrave; &#7889;p m&#7897;t h&amp;agrave;ng truy&#7873;n th&#7889;ng, c&amp;aacute;c vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#7889;p m&#7897;t c&amp;aacute;ch ng&#7851;u h&#7913;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7889;i x&#7913;ng, t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;i nh&amp;igrave;n sinh &#273;&#7897;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n kho&#7843;ng treo g&#432;&#417;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10) S&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;aacute;ch ng&#259;n k&amp;iacute;nh&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles06.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center; &quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles06.jpg&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;V&amp;aacute;ch k&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; m&#7897;t bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p ng&#259;n chia nh&#432;ng v&#7851;n tho&amp;aacute;ng, l&amp;agrave;m cho ph&amp;ograve;ng t&#7855;m c&amp;oacute; t&#7847;m m&#7855;t r&#7897;ng r&amp;atilde;i, t&amp;ocirc;n v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p c&#7911;a nh&#7919;ng b&#7913;c t&#432;&#7901;ng &#7889;p &#273;&amp;aacute; sang tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/30-bathroomtiles05.jpg',41,13,10274,'admin',1,'10-cach-phoi-mau-op-lat-gach-men-cho-nha-tam-dep','ph&#7889;i m&agrave;u g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t, g&#7841;ch men, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'ph&#7889;i m&agrave;u g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t, g&#7841;ch men, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'st',1,0,0,0),(29,'Nh&#7853;n bi&#7871;t g&#7841;ch k&eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng','C&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c c&oacute; h&#417;n 37 &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&aacute;t v&agrave; h&#7847;u h&#7871;t l&agrave;m g&#7841;ch men (ceramic). Hai n&#259;m g&#7847;n &#273;&acirc;y c&oacute; kho&#7843;ng 11 doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; m&aacute;y m&oacute;c thi&#7871;t b&#7883; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t th&ecirc;m g&#7841;ch granite (&#273;&aacute; th&#7841;ch anh nh&acirc;n t&#7841;o). &ETH;&oacute;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7921; &#432;a chu&#7897;ng c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng v&#7873; lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch granite n&agrave;y, h&agrave;ng Trung Qu&#7889;c c&ugrave;ng lo&#7841;i &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;p v&#7873; nhi&#7873;u tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7843; n&#432;&#7899;c. Gi&aacute; tu&#417;ng &#273;&#7889;i r&#7867;, m&agrave;u s&#7855;c, hoa v&#259;n kh&aacute; &#273;a d&#7841;ng nh&#432;ng ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i &ldquo;x&eacute;t l&#7841;i&rdquo;...','&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;K&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7915; kh&amp;acirc;u s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch granite k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng th&amp;igrave; c&#7889;t li&#7879;u pha tr&#7897;n v&amp;agrave; quy tr&amp;igrave;nh s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t chu&#7849;n. V&amp;iacute; d&#7909;, ph&amp;acirc;n l&#432;&#7907;ng ph&#7847;n tr&#259;m tr&amp;agrave;ng th&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t kh&amp;aacute;c nhau; ph&#7909; gia thay v&amp;igrave; nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i lo&#7841;i t&#7889;t th&amp;igrave; d&amp;ugrave;ng lo&#7841;i s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a v&amp;igrave; l&#432;&#7907;ng m&amp;agrave;u chi&#7871;m t&#7927; l&#7879; l&#7899;n; nhi&#7879;t &#273;&#7897; nung kh&amp;ocirc;ng t&#7899;i, c&amp;aacute;c ph&amp;acirc;n t&#7917; trong c&#7889;t li&#7879;u s&#7869; thi&#7871;u &#273;&#7897; k&#7871;t ch&#7863;t. T&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; &amp;ldquo;c&amp;ocirc;ng th&#7913;c&amp;rdquo; t&#7841;o x&#432;&#417;ng g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t v&amp;agrave; &#273;&amp;oacute; l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; l&amp;agrave;m gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7853;n di&#7879;n g&#7841;ch &amp;quot;y&#7871;u&amp;quot;: b&#7873; d&amp;agrave;y vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch m&#7887;ng h&#417;n v&amp;agrave; ch&#7895; d&amp;agrave;y m&#7887;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7873;u; b&#7873; m&#7863;t g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7875;m r&#7895;; m&amp;agrave;u kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7855;c, h&#417;i x&#7881;n v&amp;agrave; ph&amp;iacute;a l&#432;ng vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng in t&amp;ecirc;n nh&amp;agrave; s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7843;n ph&#7849;m k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng &amp;quot;r&amp;uacute;t&amp;quot; b&#7899;t nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u, s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ch&#7845;t li&#7879;u x&#7845;u v&amp;agrave; quy tr&amp;igrave;nh th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;quot;nghi&amp;ecirc;m&amp;quot;. So v&#7899;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m &#273;&#7841;t th&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;ng &amp;quot;y&#7871;u&amp;quot; ch&#7881; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nung t&#7915; 700 - 800oC, th&#7901;i gian nung ch&#7915;ng 32 - 35 ph&amp;uacute;t. B&#7843;n th&amp;acirc;n men oxid th&#7911;y ng&amp;acirc;n v&amp;agrave; ph&#7909; gia trong men frit lo&#7841;i t&#7889;t khi n&amp;oacute;ng ch&#7843;y s&#7869; t&#7841;o b&#7873; m&#7863;t m&#7883;n h&#417;n. Gi&#7843;m thi&#7875;u c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t n&amp;ecirc;u tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#7873;u l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng &amp;quot;bi&#7879;n ph&amp;aacute;p&amp;quot; tham gia &#273;&#7875; h&#7841; gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nh&#7853;n bi&#7871;t g&#7841;ch x&#7845;u&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;C&amp;oacute; th&#7875; nh&#7853;n di&#7879;n h&amp;agrave;ng k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t b&#7857;ng vi&#7879;c xem &#273;&#7897; d&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7873;u c&#7911;a vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch. K&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; c&amp;aacute;c vi&amp;ecirc;n sai l&#7879;ch nhi&#7873;u trong c&amp;ugrave;ng m&#7897;t l&amp;ocirc; h&amp;agrave;ng, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; th&#7845;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#7897; cong v&amp;ecirc;nh, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7859;ng; m&#7863;t men b&#7883; r&#7895;. &amp;ETH;&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;eacute;t c&#7911;a hoa v&#259;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng s&#7855;c s&#7843;o do l&#432;&#7899;i t&#7845;m l&#7909;a in kh&amp;ocirc;ng m&#7883;n v&amp;agrave; t&amp;iacute;nh &#273;&#7891;ng m&amp;agrave;u trong t&#7915;ng l&amp;ocirc; h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#7893;n &#273;&#7883;nh. H&amp;agrave;ng k&amp;eacute;m ch&#7845;t th&amp;igrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7869; mau phai, l&#7899;p men mau m&amp;ograve;n hay bong tr&amp;oacute;c v&amp;agrave; d&#7877; tr&#7847;y x&#432;&#7899;c. C&amp;aacute;ch nh&#7853;n di&#7879;n n&#7919;a l&amp;agrave; khi &#273;&#432;a g&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave;o m&amp;aacute;y c&#7855;t, h&amp;agrave;ng x&#7845;u &#273;&#7913;t ng&#7885;t v&amp;agrave; nhanh; ng&#432;&#7907;c l&#7841;i g&#7841;ch t&#7889;t, &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng c&#7855;t &#273;i ch&#7853;m.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Hi&#7879;n c&amp;aacute;c h&amp;atilde;ng l&amp;agrave;m g&#7841;ch trong n&#432;&#7899;c th&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;oacute; ph&amp;ograve;ng tr&#432;ng b&amp;agrave;y v&amp;agrave; t&#7893; t&#432; v&#7845;n kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng, gi&amp;uacute;p ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&amp;oacute; hoa v&#259;n, k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; v&amp;agrave; s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;. M&#7863;t kh&amp;aacute;c, t&#7915;ng l&amp;ocirc; h&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;acirc;n theo ng&amp;agrave;y s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t hay theo s&#7889; s&amp;ecirc;-ri n&amp;ecirc;n m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;. B&#7903;i g&#7841;ch l&amp;ocirc; tr&#432;&#7899;c v&#7899;i l&amp;ocirc; sau xu&#7845;t x&#432;&#7903;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng c&amp;oacute; s&#7921; sai l&#7879;ch m&amp;agrave;u nh&#7845;t &#273;&#7883;nh. Do v&#7853;y mua g&#7841;ch &amp;quot;tr&amp;ocirc;i n&#7893;i&amp;quot;, kh&amp;ocirc;ng r&amp;otilde; xu&#7845;t x&#7913; s&#7869; kh&amp;oacute; c&amp;oacute; s&#7855;c m&amp;agrave;u gi&#7889;ng &#273;&#7891;ng lo&#7841;t. H&#417;n n&#7919;a, m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde; h&amp;agrave;ng n&#7897;i r&#7845;t &#273;a d&#7841;ng t&#7915; h&#7885;a ti&#7871;t c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n cho &#273;&#7871;n hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i &#273;&#7873;u xu&#7845;t hi&#7879;n; c&amp;oacute; c&#7843; g&#7841;ch t&#7841;o v&amp;acirc;n &#273;&amp;aacute;, gi&#7843; g&#7841;ch t&amp;agrave;u, g&#7841;ch s&amp;acirc;n v&#432;&#7901;n, g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t c&amp;oacute; vi&#7873;n, &#273;i&#7875;m nh&#7845;n &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897;&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng g&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng tr&amp;ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng T&amp;ocirc; Hi&#7871;n Th&amp;agrave;nh, qu&#7853;n10 n&amp;oacute;i, &amp;quot;g&#7841;ch men lo&#7841;i 3 c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7851;n t&#7889;t h&#417;n g&#7841;ch Trung Qu&#7889;c v&amp;igrave; th&#432;&#7901;ng lo&#7841;i d&#7903; m&#7899;i nh&#7853;p sang &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867;. B&#7867; vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch ra, nhi&#7873;u khi c&amp;ograve;n th&#7845;y v&#7871;t x&amp;aacute;m &#273;en &#7903; gi&#7919;a x&#432;&#417;ng g&#7841;ch do nung ch&#432;a t&#7899;i. V&amp;agrave; coi ch&#7915;ng nh&#7847;m g&#7841;ch Trung Qu&#7889;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ch&amp;agrave;o l&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng &amp;ETH;&amp;agrave;i Loan!&amp;quot;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c m&#7897;t chi nh&amp;aacute;nh c&amp;ocirc;ng ty chuy&amp;ecirc;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t g&#7841;ch granite cho bi&#7871;t, &amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; &#273;i kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng g&#7841;ch t&#7841;i Trung Qu&#7889;c; c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p l&#7899;n v&#7851;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t r&#7847;m r&#7897; h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7889;t cho xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u v&amp;agrave; b&amp;aacute;n n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; cao h&#417;n h&amp;agrave;ng t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam. C&amp;ograve;n nh&#7919;ng &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; nh&#7887; b&#7883; ph&amp;aacute; s&#7843;n nhi&#7873;u, h&amp;agrave;ng h&amp;oacute;a ch&#7845;t &#273;&#7847;y b&amp;atilde;i &amp;quot;v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#273;&amp;oacute; &#273;ang &#273;&#432;&#7907;c &#273;&#432;a sang th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng Vi&#7879;t Nam&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&amp;ocirc;ng ri&amp;ecirc;ng g&amp;igrave; h&amp;agrave;ng Trung Qu&#7889;c c&amp;oacute; ph&#7849;m ch&#7845;t th&#7845;p m&amp;agrave; h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c c&#361;ng &#273;ang c&amp;oacute; nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i gi&amp;aacute; th&#7845;p v&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i trong ng&amp;agrave;nh cho bi&#7871;t, &amp;quot;ch&#7881; c&amp;oacute; gi&#7843;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng m&#7899;i c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; c&#7841;nh tranh nh&#432; v&#7853;y! V&amp;agrave; s&#7921; c&#7841;nh tranh gi&#7919;a c&amp;aacute;c doanh nghi&#7879;p trong n&#432;&#7899;c hi&#7879;n kh&amp;aacute; c&#259;ng th&#7859;ng&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#7907; l&amp;yacute; kinh doanh t&#7893;ng gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7889;c m&#7897;t c&amp;ocirc;ng ty g&#7841;ch cho bi&#7871;t, Hi&#7879;p h&#7897;i g&#7889;m s&#7913; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng &#273;&amp;atilde; c&amp;oacute; ki&#7871;n ngh&#7883; l&amp;ecirc;n B&#7897; X&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng ban h&amp;agrave;nh m&#7897;t ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n cao Vi&#7879;t Nam d&amp;agrave;nh cho c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t xu&#7845;t kh&#7849;u v&amp;agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng n&#7897;i &#273;&#7883;a. V&amp;igrave; hi&#7879;n nay, m&#7895;i &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; t&#7921; x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng m&#7897;t ti&amp;ecirc;u chu&#7849;n ri&amp;ecirc;ng cho m&amp;igrave;nh v&amp;agrave; t&#7921; ch&#7883;u tr&amp;aacute;ch nhi&#7879;m; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&#417; quan n&amp;agrave;o gi&amp;aacute;m &#273;&#7883;nh ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng. T&#7915; &#273;&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7847;u t&#432; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; c&#361; k&#7929; v&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;ch&#7855;p v&amp;aacute;&amp;rdquo; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng b&#7897; n&amp;ecirc;n c&amp;aacute;c c&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;o&#7841;n s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t y&amp;ecirc;u c&#7847;u. Ho&#7863;c &#273;&#7875; gi&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute; th&amp;agrave;nh s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m th&amp;igrave; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p gi&#7843;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng; nh&#7919;ng y&#7871;u t&#7889; &#273;&amp;oacute; g&amp;acirc;y kh&amp;oacute; kh&#259;n cho s&#7921; ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a c&#7911;a ng&#432;&#7901;i ti&amp;ecirc;u d&amp;ugrave;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/kemchatluong.jpg',41,13,8247,'admin',1,'nhan-biet-gach-kem-chat-luong','g&#7841;ch men k&eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'g&#7841;ch men k&eacute;m ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'st',1,0,0,0),(30,'C&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch men?','Tr&ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng c&oacute; nhi&#7873;u lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch men. Ngo&agrave;i ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch men ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p t&uacute;i ti&#7873;n; m&agrave;u s&#7855;c, hoa v&#259;n c&#259;n c&#7913; m&agrave;u t&#432;&#7901;ng, ki&#7871;n tr&uacute;c ng&ocirc;i nh&agrave;, b&#7841;n c&oacute; th&#7875; tham kh&#7843;o m&#7897;t s&#7889; c&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch men &#273;&#417;n gi&#7843;n ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cao d&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y.','&lt;p&gt;- L&#432;ng (b&#7873; d&amp;agrave;y) g&#7841;ch m&amp;agrave;u tr&#7855;ng (nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u l&amp;agrave; cao lanh v&amp;agrave; tr&amp;agrave;ng th&#7841;ch) t&#7889;t h&#417;n m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7887; (nguy&amp;ecirc;n li&#7879;u ch&amp;iacute;nh l&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7845;t s&amp;eacute;t).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- G&amp;otilde; nh&#7865; v&amp;agrave;o g&#7841;ch, &amp;acirc;m thanh ph&amp;aacute;t ra thanh ch&#7913;ng t&#7887; g&#7841;ch c&#7913;ng v&amp;agrave; ch&#7855;c. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng c&amp;aacute;ch n&amp;agrave;y v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Nh&#7887; v&amp;agrave;i gi&#7885;t n&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave;o l&#432;ng g&#7841;ch ph&#7847;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng tr&amp;aacute;ng men, n&#432;&#7899;c th&#7845;m c&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7853;m c&amp;agrave;ng t&#7889;t. C&amp;aacute;ch n&amp;agrave;y c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &amp;aacute;p d&#7909;ng v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- G&#7841;ch ph&#7843;i th&#7853;t ph&#7859;ng, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; &amp;uacute;p m&#7863;t 2 vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave;o nhau xem khe h&#7903; c&amp;oacute; b&#7883; cong v&amp;ecirc;nh hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- Nh&amp;igrave;n k&#7929; m&#7863;t g&#7841;ch xem c&amp;oacute; l&#7895; nh&#7887; hay kh&amp;ocirc;ng, c&amp;agrave;ng &amp;iacute;t l&#7895; (kh&amp;ocirc;ng qu&amp;aacute; 3 l&#7895;), c&amp;agrave;ng nh&#7887; (ch&#7881; b&#7857;ng &#273;&#7847;u kim m&amp;aacute;y may) c&amp;agrave;ng t&#7889;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;S&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch men&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;ecirc;n th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng hi&#7879;n nay c&amp;oacute; hai lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch men l&amp;agrave; men b&amp;oacute;ng v&amp;agrave; men m&#7901;. Lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch men b&amp;oacute;ng c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; th&#7849;m m&#7929; cao, ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i kh&amp;ocirc; r&amp;aacute;o, tho&amp;aacute;ng m&amp;aacute;t, nh&#432;ng nh&#432;&#7907;c &#273;i&#7875;m l&amp;agrave; d&#7877; b&#7883; tr&#7847;y x&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#7897; tr&#417;n tr&#432;&#7907;t cao, g&amp;acirc;y nguy hi&#7875;m cho ng&#432;&#7901;i gi&amp;agrave; v&amp;agrave; tr&#7867; em.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch men m&#7901; n&#7871;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p s&#7869; mang l&#7841;i v&#7867; &#273;&#7865;p sang tr&#7885;ng cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;, &#432;u &#273;i&#7875;m &amp;iacute;t b&#7883; tr&#7847;y x&#432;&#7899;c v&amp;agrave; ch&#7889;ng tr&#417;n tr&#432;&#7907;t. Nh&#7919;ng h&#7885;a ti&#7871;t tr&amp;ecirc;n b&#7873; m&#7863;t c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch &#273;&#432;&#7907;c thi&#7871;t k&#7871; c&amp;oacute; chi&#7873;u s&amp;acirc;u, th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p cho nh&#7919;ng ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; &amp;oacute;c s&amp;aacute;ng t&#7841;o mu&#7889;n t&#7841;o phong c&amp;aacute;ch cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;S&#7921; h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a gi&#7919;a m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch n&#7873;n, t&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng &#273;&amp;egrave;n s&#7869; l&amp;agrave;m ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch th&amp;ecirc;m &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng, sang tr&#7885;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;G&#7841;ch men c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905;, t&#7915; 5 x 5cm &#273;&#7871;n 45 x 45cm. Lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch vu&amp;ocirc;ng v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; 30 x 30cm hay 40 x 40cm th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p &#273;&#7875; l&amp;oacute;t s&amp;agrave;n nh&amp;agrave;, lo&#7841;i h&amp;igrave;nh ch&#7919; nh&#7853;t v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905; 20 x 25cm hay 25 x 40cm th&#432;&#7901;ng d&amp;ugrave;ng &#273;&#7875; &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng. Khi l&amp;aacute;t g&#7841;ch c&#7847;n l&#432;u &amp;yacute;, n&#7871;u chi&#7873;u ngang c&#7911;a n&#7873;n nh&amp;agrave; nh&#7887; h&#417;n 4 m&amp;eacute;t c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 30 x 30cm, 33 x 33cm k&#7871;t h&#7907;p c&amp;aacute;ch l&amp;aacute;t x&amp;eacute;o s&#7869; l&amp;agrave;m kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian tr&amp;ocirc;ng r&#7897;ng h&#417;n.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p n&#7873;n nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; chi&#7873;u ngang h&#417;n 4m, ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; t&amp;ugrave;y th&amp;iacute;ch ch&#7885;n l&#7921;a nh&#7919;ng lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c l&#7899;n nh&#432; 40 x 40cm, 60 x 60cm hay 80 x 80cm. &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian mang &#273;&#7853;m n&amp;eacute;t c&#7893; &#273;i&#7875;n, &#273;&#7891; trang tr&amp;iacute; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t b&#7857;ng g&#7895; th&amp;igrave; lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch gi&#7843; c&#7893; v&#7899;i k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 33 x 33cm, c&amp;oacute; vi&#7873;n g&amp;oacute;c s&#7855;c s&#7843;o l&amp;agrave; th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p nh&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Ngo&amp;agrave;i k&amp;iacute;ch c&#7905;, c&#7847;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; &#273;&#7871;n m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c c&#7911;a g&#7841;ch cho h&amp;agrave;i h&amp;ograve;a v&#7899;i m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a t&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave;, c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c v&#7853;t d&#7909;ng trang tr&amp;iacute; c&#361;ng nh&#432; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i ch&#7913;c n&#259;ng c&#7911;a t&#7915;ng ph&amp;ograve;ng, t&#7915;ng khu v&#7921;c trong &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n &amp;aacute;nh s&amp;aacute;ng kh&amp;aacute;c nhau. S&#7921; &#273;&#7889;i ch&#7885;i v&#7873; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c s&#7869; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7921; b&#7913;c b&#7889;i, kh&amp;ocirc;ng tho&#7843;i m&amp;aacute;i. M&amp;agrave;u g&#7841;ch s&amp;aacute;ng th&amp;iacute;ch h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; c&amp;aacute;c m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#7901;ng. N&#7871;u ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch m&amp;agrave;u t&#7889;i c&#7847;n l&#432;u &amp;yacute; cho ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i m&amp;agrave;u c&#7911;a t&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Trong ph&amp;ograve;ng kh&amp;aacute;ch, ph&amp;ograve;ng &#259;n, khu v&#7921;c sinh ho&#7841;t chung c&#7911;a gia &#273;&amp;igrave;nh, ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; gam m&amp;agrave;u &#7845;m nh&#432; v&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7845;t, n&amp;acirc;u k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#432;&#7901;ng m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o s&#7921; &#7845;m c&amp;uacute;ng, th&amp;acirc;n m&#7853;t. Khu v&#7921;c ph&amp;ograve;ng em b&amp;eacute;, ph&amp;ograve;ng gi&#7843;i tr&amp;iacute; c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch m&amp;agrave;u v&amp;agrave;ng k&#7871;t h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#432;&#7901;ng m&amp;agrave;u xanh ng&#7885;c.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;N&#7871;u t&#432;&#7901;ng nh&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u xanh l&amp;aacute;, c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; k&#7871;t h&#7907;p g&#7841;ch m&amp;agrave;u n&amp;acirc;u, kem, xanh l&amp;aacute; t&amp;ugrave;y theo s&#7903; th&amp;iacute;ch c&#7911;a ch&#7911; nh&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o n&amp;ecirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng gian mang &#273;&#7853;m s&#7855;c th&amp;aacute;i thi&amp;ecirc;n nhi&amp;ecirc;n, l&amp;atilde;ng m&#7841;n hay hi&#7879;n &#273;&#7841;i. Tr&#432;&#7901;ng h&#7907;p c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch nh&#7887; th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;aacute;t g&#7841;ch ph&#7913;c t&#7841;p, ch&#7881; c&#7847;n ch&#7885;n m&#7897;t gam m&amp;agrave;u ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p. &#7902; khu v&#7921;c ngo&amp;agrave;i tr&#7901;i, nh&#7919;ng n&#417;i d&#7877; b&amp;aacute;m b&#7909;i, th&#7845;m n&#432;&#7899;c n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7853;m, &#273;&#7897; c&#7913;ng cao, &amp;iacute;t tr&#417;n tr&#432;&#7907;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/news/10-2011/32-ceramic.jpg',41,13,6897,'admin',1,'cach-chon-gach-men?','c&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch men, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'c&aacute;ch ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch men, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Theo archi',1,0,0,0),(31,'L&#432;u &yacute; khi mua v&agrave; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch men','C&#259;n nh&agrave; c&#7911;a b&#7841;n s&#7869; &#273;&#7865;p h&#417;n n&#7871;u g&#7841;ch l&aacute;t n&#7873;n &#273;&#7865;p, trang nh&atilde;. Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nhi&#7873;u ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#7841;i kh&ocirc;ng bi&#7871;t ch&#7885;n, l&aacute;t g&#7841;ch c&oacute; m&agrave;u t&#432;&#417;ng ph&#7843;n v&#7899;i t&#432;&#7901;ng, tr&ocirc;ng r&#7845;t x&#7845;u. D&#432;&#7899;i &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; m&#7897;t v&agrave;i ch&uacute; &yacute;, b&#7841;n n&ecirc;n tham kh&#7843;o.','&lt;p&gt;- &#272;&#7889;i v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch d&#432;&#7899;i 30 m2, chi&#7873;u ngang h&#7865;p, b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 300 x 300 mm. T&#7889;t nh&#7845;t l&amp;agrave; n&amp;ecirc;n d&amp;ugrave;ng g&#7841;ch m&#7897;t m&amp;agrave;u ho&#7863;c hoa &#273;&#417;n &#273;&#7875; t&#7841;o c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng th&amp;ecirc;m r&#7897;ng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- V&#7899;i c&#259;n ph&amp;ograve;ng c&amp;oacute; di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch tr&amp;ecirc;n 30 m2, b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c 400 x 400 mm ho&#7863;c 500 x 500 mm. M&amp;agrave;u g&#7841;ch s&amp;aacute;ng ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i t&#7845;t c&#7843; m&amp;agrave;u t&#432;&#7901;ng. N&#7871;u b&#7841;n ch&#7885;n lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch c&amp;oacute; m&amp;agrave;u t&#7889;i, c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&#432;u &amp;yacute; &#273;&#7871;n s&#417;n, v&amp;ocirc;i t&#432;&#7901;ng v&amp;agrave; &#273;&#7891; n&#7897;i th&#7845;t. Kh&amp;ocirc;ng n&amp;ecirc;n ch&#7885;n m&amp;agrave;u &#273;&#7889;i ch&#7885;i, s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y c&#7843;m gi&amp;aacute;c b&#7913;c b&#7889;i, kh&amp;ocirc;ng tho&#7843;i m&amp;aacute;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;C&amp;aacute;c b&#432;&#7899;c l&amp;aacute;t n&#7873;n&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &lt;em&gt;Ki&#7875;m tra g&#7841;ch men:&lt;/em&gt; Tr&#432;&#7899;c khi s&#7917; d&#7909;ng g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t, b&#7841;n n&amp;ecirc;n ki&#7875;m tra ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m. N&#7871;u k&amp;iacute;ch th&#432;&#7899;c kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7891;ng &#273;&#7873;u, cong v&amp;ecirc;nh l&amp;agrave;m cho n&#7873;n nh&amp;agrave; b&#7883; x&#7845;u &#273;i. Khi &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t t&#432;&#7901;ng c&#361;ng c&#7847;n ch&amp;uacute; &amp;yacute; &#273;&#7871;n di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch d&amp;iacute;nh c&#7911;a c&amp;aacute;c r&amp;atilde;nh &#7903; m&#7863;t sau vi&amp;ecirc;n g&#7841;ch. B&#7903;i n&#7871;u di&#7879;n t&amp;iacute;ch kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#7911; l&#7899;n s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y th&#7845;m hay bong g&#7841;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &lt;em&gt;Tu s&#7917;a b&#7873; m&#7863;t x&amp;acirc;y d&#7921;ng:&lt;/em&gt; &#272;&amp;acirc;y l&amp;agrave; vi&#7879;c c&#7847;n ph&#7843;i l&amp;agrave;m tr&#432;&#7899;c khi &#7889;p v&amp;agrave; l&amp;aacute;t g&#7841;ch. Ngo&amp;agrave;i vi&#7879;c tr&amp;aacute;m v&#7919;a nhi&#7873;u l&#7847;n l&amp;agrave;m cho b&#7873; m&#7863;t ph&#7859;ng, b&#7841;n c&#7847;n r&#7917;a c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7895; b&#7849;n do v&amp;aacute;n c&#7889;t pha g&amp;acirc;y ra.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &lt;em&gt;L&amp;agrave;m ph&#7859;ng l&#7899;p l&amp;oacute;t:&lt;/em&gt; Tr&#7897;n &#273;&#7873;u c&amp;aacute;t s&#7841;ch v&amp;agrave; xi m&#259;ng t&#7889;t (ngo&amp;agrave;i ra c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; tr&#7897;n c&amp;aacute;c ch&#7845;t t&#259;ng &#273;&#7897; d&#7867;o, ch&#7889;ng co r&amp;uacute;t) sau &#273;&amp;oacute; tr&amp;aacute;m ph&#7859;ng b&#7873; m&#7863;t. Tr&amp;aacute;nh &#273;&#7875; v&#7919;a &#273;&amp;oacute;ng c&#7909;c, khi l&amp;aacute;t s&#7869; g&amp;acirc;y cong v&amp;ecirc;nh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;- &lt;em&gt;&#7888;p l&amp;aacute;t v&amp;agrave; mi&#7871;t m&#7841;ch:&lt;/em&gt; Th&amp;ocirc;ng th&#432;&#7901;ng th&#7901;i gian k&#7871;t d&amp;iacute;nh t&#7889;t nh&#7845;t t&#7915; 15 &#273;&#7871;n 20 ph&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i xi m&#259;ng c&amp;oacute; tr&#7897;n b&#7897;t ch&#7889;ng ng&#432;ng k&#7871;t, kho&#7843;ng 25-35 ph&amp;uacute;t &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i xi m&#259;ng c&amp;oacute; tr&#7897;n h&#7895;n h&#7907;p keo gi&#7919; n&#432;&#7899;c ch&#7889;ng co. Sau khi &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t xong, mi&#7871;t xi m&#259;ng tr&#7855;ng v&amp;agrave;o c&amp;aacute;c khe m&#7841;ch.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','',41,13,6264,'admin',1,'luu-y-khi-mua-va-su-dung-gach-men','l&#432;u &yacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, mikado ceramic, g&#7841;ch men',NULL,NULL,NULL,'l&#432;u &yacute; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng, mikado ceramic, g&#7841;ch men',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Theo t&#432; v&#7845;n ti&ecirc;u d&ugrave;ng',1,0,0,0),(32,'Nh&agrave; n&ocirc;ng ch&#7885;n VLXD: H&agrave;ng n&#7897;i gi&aacute; r&#7867; l&ecirc;n ng&ocirc;i','Th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;n v&agrave;o m&ugrave;a x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng di&#7877;n ra khung c&#7843;nh mua s&#7855;m VLXD t&#7845;p n&#7853;p kh&ocirc;ng k&eacute;m g&igrave; &#7903; nh&#7919;ng TP l&#7899;n, Tuy nhi&ecirc;n, nh&oacute;m h&agrave;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7851;n l&agrave; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m trong n&#432;&#7899;c v&#7899;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t v&agrave; gi&aacute; c&#7843; &ldquo;v&#7915;a ph&#7843;i&rdquo;. Ch&iacute;nh b&#7903;i v&#7853;y, ch&#7895; &#273;&#7913;ng cho th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng VLXD n&ocirc;ng th&ocirc;n ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; h&agrave;ng n&#7897;i.','&lt;p&gt;Tr&amp;aacute;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;ch l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u x&amp;acirc;y ph&#7843;i &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o ti&amp;ecirc;u ch&amp;iacute; &amp;ldquo;&#273;&#7855;t m&#7845;y c&#361;ng mua mi&#7877;n l&amp;agrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t&amp;rdquo; th&amp;igrave; khi ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n n&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;ocirc;n l&#7841;i &#273;&#432;a ra ti&amp;ecirc;u ch&amp;iacute; &#273;&#7847;u ti&amp;ecirc;n l&amp;agrave; &amp;ldquo;gi&amp;aacute; c&#7843; v&#7915;a ph&#7843;i v&#7899;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng v&#7915;a t&#7847;m&amp;rdquo;. L&amp;yacute; do &#273;&#432;a ra c&#361;ng kh&amp;aacute; d&#7877; hi&#7875;u b&#7903;i s&#7889; ti&#7873;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi cho m&#7895;i c&#259;n h&#7897; m&#7899;i n&#7857;m trong kho&#7843;ng 500-800 tri&#7879;u &#273;/c&#259;n (kho&#7843;ng 70-100m&amp;sup2;), trong &#273;&amp;oacute;, v&#7853;t li&#7879;u &#273;&amp;atilde; chi&#7871;m 70-80% chi ph&amp;iacute;. B&#7903;i v&#7853;y, ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u l&amp;aacute;t s&amp;agrave;n, ng&amp;oacute;i l&#7907;p, g&#7841;ch &#7889;p t&#432;&#7901;ng hay thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&amp;iacute;nh to&amp;aacute;n sao cho v&#7915;a v&#7863;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; ti&#7873;n b&#7887; ra. &#272;ang chu&#7849;n b&#7883; ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ho&amp;agrave;n thi&#7879;n cho ng&amp;ocirc;i nh&amp;agrave; m&#7899;i, anh L&#7841;i V&#259;n Minh (x&amp;atilde; Kinh K&#7879; - huy&#7879;n L&amp;acirc;m Thao - Ph&amp;uacute; Th&#7885;) cho bi&#7871;t: Ch&#7855;c ch&#7855;n l&amp;agrave; t&amp;ocirc;i ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a Vi&#7879;t Nam s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&amp;igrave; ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#361;ng t&#7889;t m&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; l&#7841;i ph&#7843;i ch&#259;ng. C&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m gi&amp;aacute; cao v&#7899;i ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t h&#417;n c&amp;oacute; th&#7875; s&#7917; d&#7909;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a VIGLACERA, MIKADO,...&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Tuy&#7871;n ph&#7889; L&amp;acirc;m Thao (Ph&amp;uacute; Th&#7885;) d&amp;agrave;i ch&#7915;ng 5km c&amp;oacute; h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7909;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng, &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; VLXD m&#7885;c l&amp;ecirc;n. Kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t qua c&amp;aacute;c c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng th&amp;igrave; th&#7845;y c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m VLXD &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&amp;aacute;n kh&amp;aacute; phong ph&amp;uacute; v&#7873; ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i v&amp;agrave; m&#7851;u m&amp;atilde;. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, ch&#7911; y&#7871;u nh&#7919;ng s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&amp;agrave;y &#273;&#432;&#7907;c nh&#7853;p t&#7915; c&amp;aacute;c Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m g&#7841;ch men, g&#7841;ch &#7889;p l&amp;aacute;t, ng&amp;oacute;i l&#7907;p c&#7911;a Prime, MIKADO, VIGLACERA&amp;hellip;; thi&#7871;t b&#7883; v&#7879; sinh c&#7911;a VIGLACERA, Inax, ToTo v&amp;agrave; nh&#7853;p kh&#7849;u t&#7915; Trung Qu&#7889;c. C&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m cao c&#7845;p h&#417;n g&#7841;ch granite, v&amp;aacute;n l&amp;aacute;t s&amp;agrave;n hay v&#7853;t li&#7879;u ti&#7875;u c&#7843;nh trang tr&amp;iacute;&amp;hellip; th&#432;&#7901;ng &amp;iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&amp;agrave;y b&amp;aacute;n. Ngay c&#7843; v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; l&#7899;n chuy&amp;ecirc;n cung c&#7845;p s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a MIKADO, VIGLACERA c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i b&amp;aacute;n th&amp;ecirc;m c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m c&#7911;a Cty trong n&#432;&#7899;c &#273;&#7875; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n. Anh Nguy&#7877;n Duy H&#7843;i - ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng VLXD Anh Anh (huy&#7879;n L&amp;acirc;m Thao) cho bi&#7871;t: X&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7883;nh kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7911; y&#7871;u l&amp;agrave; nh&#7919;ng ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n c&amp;oacute; m&#7913;c thu nh&#7853;p trung b&amp;igrave;nh n&amp;ecirc;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i nh&#7853;p v&#7873; l&amp;agrave; c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m gi&amp;aacute; v&#7915;a t&#7847;m nh&#432;ng ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng c&#361;ng ph&#7843;i t&#7889;t. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i v&amp;igrave; gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; m&amp;agrave; m&amp;agrave;u s&#7855;c v&amp;agrave; ch&#7911;ng lo&#7841;i kh&amp;ocirc;ng phong ph&amp;uacute;. Th&#432;&#7901;ng th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng c&#361;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; nhi&#7873;u &#273;i&#7873;u ki&#7879;n t&amp;igrave;m hi&#7875;u v&amp;agrave; so s&amp;aacute;nh c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m n&#7871;u nh&#432; kh&amp;ocirc;ng c&amp;oacute; t&#432; v&#7845;n c&#7911;a ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng, n&amp;ecirc;n h&#7885; hay ch&#7885;n v&#7853;t li&#7879;u qua gi&#7899;i thi&#7879;u ho&#7863;c &#273;&#432;&#7907;c qu&#7843;ng c&amp;aacute;o tr&amp;ecirc;n tivi. C&amp;ograve;n &#273;&#7889;i v&#7899;i v&amp;aacute;n s&amp;agrave;n, hay thi&#7871;t b&#7883; nh&amp;agrave; t&#7855;m nh&#7853;p ngo&#7841;i th&amp;igrave; kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng nhi&#7873;u n&amp;ecirc;n ch&amp;uacute;ng t&amp;ocirc;i ch&#7881; nh&#7853;p v&#7873; &#273;&#7875; b&amp;aacute;n v&#7899;i s&#7889; l&#432;&#7907;ng nh&#7887; ph&#7909;c v&#7909; cho kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;aacute; gi&#7843; tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889;. G&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t Trung Qu&#7889;c c&amp;agrave;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;igrave; ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n ch&#432;a quen v&#7899;i g&#7841;ch men l&amp;aacute;t kh&#7893; l&#7899;n (80x80 cm) v&amp;agrave; gi&amp;aacute; c&#361;ng kh&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;Kh&#7843;o s&amp;aacute;t gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&amp;aacute;c s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m VLXD tr&amp;ecirc;n tuy&#7871;n ph&#7889; L&amp;acirc;m Thao qua c&amp;aacute;c &#273;&#7841;i l&amp;yacute; &amp;nbsp;th&amp;igrave; c&amp;aacute;c m&#7863;t h&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7881; ch&amp;ecirc;nh nhau ch&amp;uacute;t &amp;iacute;t. Ch&#7883; Ph&#432;&#7907;ng Loan (ch&#7911; c&#7917;a h&amp;agrave;ng kinh doanh tr&amp;ecirc;n ph&#7889; L&amp;acirc;m Thao) cho bi&#7871;t: Gi&amp;aacute; b&amp;aacute;n c&#7911;a m&#7895;i lo&#7841;i s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m s&#7869; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ph&amp;acirc;n lo&#7841;i t&#7915; lo&#7841;i t&#7889;t &#273;&#7871;n lo&#7841;i trung b&amp;igrave;nh (t&#7915; A1-A3) &#273;&#7875; ph&amp;ugrave; h&#7907;p nhu c&#7847;u s&#7917; d&#7909;ng c&#7911;a kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng. T&#7915; &#273;&#7847;u n&#259;m &#273;&#7871;n gi&#7901;, gi&amp;aacute; m&#7897;t s&#7889; s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m nh&#432; g&#7841;ch men, ng&amp;oacute;i l&#7907;p c&amp;oacute; t&#259;ng gi&amp;aacute;, nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng ph&#7843;i v&amp;igrave; th&#7871; m&amp;agrave; s&#7913;c mua gi&#7843;m &#273;i m&amp;agrave; kh&amp;aacute;ch h&amp;agrave;ng s&#7869; ch&#7885;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m r&#7867; h&#417;n th&amp;ocirc;i.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;T&#7841;i &#273;&amp;acirc;y, h&#7847;u h&#7871;t gi&amp;aacute; g&#7841;ch men l&amp;aacute;t s&amp;agrave;n &#273;&#432;&#7907;c ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&#7899;i c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i hoa v&#259;n, nh&amp;aacute;m, men b&amp;oacute;ng&amp;hellip; c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; t&#7915; 60-80 ngh&amp;igrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng/m2 (cho lo&#7841;i 40x40 cm hay 50x50 cm); ng&amp;oacute;i l&#7907;p c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; 5,5-10 ngh&amp;igrave;n &#273;&#7891;ng/vi&amp;ecirc;n (t&amp;ugrave;y lo&#7841;i)&amp;hellip; B&amp;ecirc;n c&#7841;nh &#273;&amp;oacute;, c&amp;aacute;c lo&#7841;i g&#7841;ch l&amp;aacute;t cao c&#7845;p c&amp;oacute; gi&amp;aacute; t&#7915; tr&amp;ecirc;n 100 - 300 ngh&amp;igrave;n/m2 l&#7841;i &amp;iacute;t &#273;&#432;&#7907;c s&#7917; d&#7909;ng v&amp;igrave; qu&amp;aacute; &#273;&#7855;t. Tuy nhi&amp;ecirc;n, &#273;&#7875; c&amp;oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c c&#259;n nh&amp;agrave; b&#7873;n v&#7919;ng v&#7899;i th&#7901;i gian, ng&#432;&#7901;i d&amp;acirc;n n&amp;ocirc;ng th&amp;ocirc;n kh&amp;ocirc;ng d&#7877; d&amp;agrave;ng ch&#7845;p nh&#7853;n s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m r&#7867; nh&#432;ng kh&amp;ocirc;ng r&amp;otilde; ngu&#7891;n g&#7889;c xu&#7845;t x&#7913;. Do v&#7853;y, s&#7843;n ph&#7849;m s&#7843;n xu&#7845;t trong n&#432;&#7899;c, ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng t&#7889;t, gi&amp;aacute; r&#7867; lu&amp;ocirc;n l&amp;agrave; s&#7921; l&#7921;a ch&#7885;n s&#7889; 1 c&#7911;a th&#7883; tr&#432;&#7901;ng n&amp;agrave;y.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n','23/10/2011','23/10/2011','/home/uploads/image/gach-men/gach-lat/500x500/MS503277890.jpg',23,2,2943,'admin',1,'nha-nong-chon-vlxd-hang-noi-gia-re-len-ngoi','h&agrave;ng n&#7897;i gi&aacute; r&#7867;, mikado ceramic',NULL,NULL,NULL,'h&agrave;ng n&#7897;i gi&aacute; r&#7867;, mikado ceramic',0,0,0,'','','',4,'Theo baoxaydung',1,0,0,0),(33,'C&#7917;a h&agrave;ng H&#432;ng Nam - TP B&#7855;c Giang.','C&#7917;a h&agrave;ng H&#432;ng Nam, &#273;&#7883;a ch&#7881;: C&#7909;m c&ocirc;ng nghi&#7879;p X&#432;&#417;ng Giang II - &#272;&#432;&#7901;ng X&#432;&#417;ng Giang -TP B&#7855;c Giang.','\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;\r\n&lt;w:WordDocument&gt;\r\n&lt;w:View&gt;Normal&lt;/w:View&gt;\r\n&lt;w:Zoom&gt;0&lt;/w:Zoom&gt;\r\n&lt;w:PunctuationKerning /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:ValidateAgainstSchemas /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:SaveIfXMLInvalid&gt;false&lt;/w:SaveIfXMLInvalid&gt;\r\n&lt;w:IgnoreMixedContent&gt;false&lt;/w:IgnoreMixedContent&gt;\r\n&lt;w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText&gt;false&lt;/w:AlwaysShowPlaceholderText&gt;\r\n&lt;w:Compatibility&gt;\r\n&lt;w:BreakWrappedTables /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:SnapToGridInCell /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:WrapTextWithPunct /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:UseAsianBreakRules /&gt;\r\n&lt;w:DontGrowAutofit /&gt;\r\n&lt;/w:Compatibility&gt;\r\n&lt;w:BrowserLevel&gt;MicrosoftInternetExplorer4&lt;/w:BrowserLevel&gt;\r\n&lt;/w:WordDocument&gt;\r\n&lt;/xml&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 9]&gt;&lt;xml&gt;\r\n&lt;w:LatentStyles DefLockedState=&quot;false&quot; LatentStyleCount=&quot;156&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/w:LatentStyles&gt;\r\n&lt;/xml&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;!--[if !mso]&gt;&lt;object\r\nclassid=&quot;clsid:38481807-CA0E-42D2-BF39-B33AF135CC4D&quot; id=ieooui&gt;&lt;/object&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\nst1\\:*{behavior:url(#ieooui) }\r\n&lt;/style&gt;\r\n&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;!--[if gte mso 10]&gt;\r\n&lt;style&gt;\r\n/* Style Definitions */\r\ntable.MsoNormalTable\r\n{mso-style-name:&quot;Table Normal&quot;;\r\nmso-tstyle-rowband-size:0;\r\nmso-tstyle-colband-size:0;\r\nmso-style-noshow:yes;\r\nmso-style-parent:&quot;&quot;;\r\nmso-padding-alt:0in 5.4pt 0in 5.4pt;\r\nmso-para-margin:0in;\r\nmso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt;\r\nmso-pagination:widow-orphan;\r\nfont-size:10.0pt